pageContext.claim: “But [Pelosi] was mumbling behind me all night long [at the State of the Union]. So you know, they gave me -- I got very nice reviews on the speech, but I said even better because she was mumbling all night long behind me.”
pageContext.analysis: In video of Trump’s third State of the Union, Pelosi does appear to say something on occasion under hear breath but she is hardly “mumbling all night long.”
